description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for SKU Scope for pricing plans.
[``botocore``] Added minimum value to AutomaticStopTimeMinutes parameter.
[``botocore``] Add support for AWS Marketplace product IDs as input during CreateImageRecipe for the parent-image parameter. Add support for listing third-party components.
[``botocore``] Network Firewall now allows creation of dual stack endpoints, enabling inspection of IPv6 traffic.
